    <div id="container"><div class="build"><header id="header" class=" " style="opacity: 1; visibility: visible;"><div class="inner"><h1><a href="/" class="logo"><i class="blind">Spacecoin</i></a></h1><button type="button" class="visual-toggle"><span></span></button><div class="nav"><nav><div class="dimmed"></div><a href="/" class="active"><span>Home</span></a><a href="/satellite-tracker" class=""><span>Satellite Tracker</span></a><a href="/airdrop"><span>Airdrop</span></a><div class="button-x"><a href="https://x.com/_spacecoin" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" title="Opens a new tab"><span>@_spacecoin</span></a></div></nav></div></div></header><div class="home"><section id="spot"><div id="earth" style="transform: translateY(0px);"><video class="pc-video" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="auto"><source src="/assets/spacecoin_web-Zpfd9V_2.mp4" type="video/mp4">Your browser does not support the video tag.</video><video class="mobile-video" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="auto"><source src="/assets/spacecoin_app-hh7lNpav.mp4" type="video/mp4">Your browser does not support the video tag.</video></div><section class="content" style="transform: translateY(0px);"><div class="inner"><h2>The World’s First DePIN <span>Powered By Satellites</span></h2><p>Our decentralized satellite constellation provides global 5G internet access to the 2.9 billion people who remain unconnected.</p><div class="button-area"><a href="#signUP">Join Launch List</a><a href="/white-paper" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" class="type2"><span>Read Whitepaper</span></a></div></div></section></section><div id="content"><section class="section connecting-he-unconnected"><div class="inner"><h3>Connecting <strong>The Unconnected</strong></h3><p>Spacecoin™ is the world’s first decentralized physical infrastructure network (DePIN) powered by blockchain-enabled LEO nanosatellite constellations, positioned to become the standard open protocol for trustless internet connectivity on a global scale - connecting everyone and everything. </p></div></section><section class="section why-spacecoin-matters" style="padding-bottom: 0px;"><div class="inner"><h3>Why Spacecoin™ Matters</h3><div class="box"><dl><dt>Physically Decentralized</dt><dd>By using a constellation of small LEO satellites to create a global 5G network, this physical decentralization eliminates reliance on central authorities, reducing censorship risks and service outages while ensuring coverage in remote areas.</dd></dl><dl><dt>Transparent &amp; Trustless</dt><dd>Blockchain technology powers Spacecoin’s decentralized network, enabling transparent satellite operations with smart contracts. It manages data transmissions securely on-chain, ensuring a trustless, scalable, and resilient system without a central authority.</dd></dl><dl><dt>Borderlessly Accessible</dt><dd>By enabling a blockchain-native system that allows users to pay network fees with cryptocurrency, it removes financial and country borders, even in regions with limited banking infrastructure.</dd></dl></div></div></section><div class="divider"></div><section class="section built-on-creditcoin" style="padding-top: 0px;"><div class="inner"><h3>Built on <strong>Creditcoin</strong></h3><p>Unlocking unique benefits with Creditcoin</p><div class="box"><dl><dt>Universal Smart Contract</dt><dd>With Creditcoin's built-in Universal Smart Contract layer, it enables Spacecoin™ users to pay their internet fees with on-chain assets across multiple networks, without the need for bridging, for a user-friendly experience.</dd></dl><dl><dt>Buy Now, Pay Later</dt><dd>Users can BNPL their internet fees through Credal, a flexible payment solution that can benefit individuals living in emerging markets.</dd></dl><dl><dt>On-Chain Credit</dt><dd>Unbanked users can build their on-chain credit profiles simply by using and paying for Spacecoin's internet. By building their credit profile, it opens up greater financial accessibility and opportunity.</dd></dl></div></div></section><section class="section tracking-satellites"><div class="inner title-area"><h3>Follow The Signal: <strong>Tracking Satellites</strong></h3><p>Explore the real-time journeys of our satellites around the globe.</p><a class="button-common" href="/satellite-tracker" data-discover="true"><span>See Full Screen</span></a></div><div class="video"><div class="inner"><video autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="auto"><source src="/assets/spacecoin_satellite-C_YSpJPi.mp4" type="video/mp4">Your browser does not support the video tag.</video></div></div></section><section class="section spacecoins-roadmap"><div class="inner"><h3>Spacecoin™'s Roadmap</h3><div class="roadmap"><dl class="item-2024"><dt>2024</dt><dd>Launch Spacecoin's first satellite, CTC-0, on SpaceX's Bandwagon-2 rocket to conduct a pilot test with partners in Africa and South Asia.</dd></dl><dl class="item-2025"><dt>2025</dt><dd>Launch additional satellites to conduct pilot tests across various frequency bands, secure more partners to drive market adoption and expansion, and prepare for a Q4 launch to start providing service to billions of unconnected people.</dd></dl><dl class="item-2026"><dt>2026</dt><dd>Continually expand coverage and prepare to introduce a service that enables users to launch their own satellites and join the network.</dd></dl></div></div></section><section id="signUP" class="section sign-up"><div class="inner"><h3>Sign Up For The Launch List!</h3><form action="https://gluwa.us19.list-manage.com/subscribe/post" method="POST" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"><input type="hidden" name="u" value="04ec8cbf196526ae0b321b30d"><input type="hidden" name="id" value="bb3a757c71"><input type="hidden" name="MERGE1" value="spacecoin.org"><input type="hidden" name="tags" value="9578170"><div class="email-form"><div class="email-input"><input type="email" class="inp" name="MERGE0" placeholder="Enter your email" value=""><bu